		<p>10.2 SuTL shall have the right to either suspend or terminate this Agreement with immediate effect if it should be discovered, through third party complaints or through SuTL’s internal monitoring procedures, if Client is sending any SPAM messages through the Services. If SuTL suspends a Client’s account then Client will have to rectify any damage caused, either to SuTL’s reputation or to a third party, and will have to commit to not sending any further SPAM through the Services. If SuTL terminates a Client’s account under this clause 10.2, SuTL’s decision will be final.</p>
